      "title": "A gas ship to Colombo today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas Company says that a ship carrying 3700 metric tons of gas reached Colombo today (12th).",
        "The company states that the unloading of gas will begin this afternoon and that several more gas ships will arrive in Sri Lanka in the near future."
      ],
